<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }} - Page not found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center; /* Center content horizontally */
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left; /* Reset text alignment for the container */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: left;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
            padding-left: 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .options {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .options a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .options a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .image-container {
            float: right; /* Float the image to the right */
            width: 200px; /* Adjust as needed */
            margin-left: 20px; /* Add some space between text and image */
        }

        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%; /* Make the image responsive */
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 50%; /* Make the image circular */
        }

        .clearfix::after {
            content: "";
            display: table;
            clear: both; /* Clear the float */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container clearfix">
        <h1>Error 404 - Page not found</h1>

        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="https://sitechecker.pro/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/404-status-code.png" alt="404 Image">
        </div>

        <p>This might be because:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>You have typed the web address incorrectly, or</li>
            <li>The page you were looking for may have been moved, updated or deleted.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="options">
            <p>Please try the following options instead:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Use the search box above to see if it's available elsewhere.</li>
                <li>Use our <a href="/">site index</a>.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>